  "id": "J9WQjGvg",
  "slug": "strata-forge",
  "title": "Strata (Forge Edition)",
  "description": "A mod that adds various types of rocks into the game.",
  "body": "<p>&nbsp;<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/295/424/strata-title-card.png\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/joCZSo6.png\" width=\"1126\" height=\"18\" /></span></strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">📖 About:</span></strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">Strata is a mod that adds various types of rocks into the game. It changes the look and feel of the game and gives you a plethora of blocks to interact with.<br />The blocks are purely decorative and serve no other purpose. Strata only works exclusively with <strong><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/terraforged\">TerraForged</a></strong> and it's world type so be sure to install this as well. More information can be found on the Github page of&nbsp;<strong><a href=\"https://github.com/Quizer9O8/Strata\">Strata</a></strong> and the <strong><a href=\"https://github.com/Quizer9O8/Strata/wiki\">Wiki</a></strong>.</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/joCZSo6.png\" width=\"1126\" height=\"18\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>📦 Compatibility:</strong></span></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/terraforged\">TerraForged</a></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/joCZSo6.png\" width=\"1126\" height=\"18\" /></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">🌎 <strong>World Gen:</strong><br /></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>NOTE: This section is subject to change due to the 1.1.0 release of Strata.</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">There are a total of 15 new type of stones that can spawn anywhere in the world. They are categorized into 3 distinguished major rock types:</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><strong>Igneous Rocks</strong></span></p>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/302/112/basalt-tileset.png\" alt=\"Igneous Rocks\" width=\"1903\" height=\"1008\" /><strong>Basalt</strong></p>\n<p><strong><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/302/113/gabbro-tileset.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1125\" height=\"596\" />Gabbro</strong></p>\n</div>\n<p><strong>Metamorphic Rocks</strong></p>\n<div class=\"spoiler\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><strong><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/302/114/amphibolite-tileset.png\" alt=\"Metamorphic Rocks\" width=\"1903\" height=\"1008\" /></strong></span><hr /><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><strong>Amphibolite</strong></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><strong><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/302/115/gneiss-tileset.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1113\" height=\"590\" /></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><strong>Gneiss<br /><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/302/116/schist-tileset.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1113\" height=\"590\" /></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><strong>Schist<br /></strong></span></div>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><strong>Sedimentary</strong> <strong>Rocks</strong></span></p>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/302/117/limestone-tileset.png\" alt=\"Sedimentary Rocks\" width=\"1903\" height=\"1008\" /></span></p>\n<hr /><hr />\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><strong>Limestone<br /><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/302/118/shale-tileset.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1113\" height=\"590\" /></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><strong>Shale</strong></span></p>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><br /></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">📷 <strong>Screenshots: </strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Terrain</strong></span></p>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p><strong><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/295/439/2020-06-02_15.png\" alt=\"Limestone/Diorite Torridonian Fells\" width=\"1903\" height=\"1008\" /></strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;<strong><br /></strong></p>\n<p><strong><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/295/488/2020-06-02_21.png\" alt=\"Amphibolite Plateau\" width=\"1903\" height=\"1008\" /></strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;<strong><br /></strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/295/486/2020-06-02_21.png\" alt=\"Schist Mountains\" width=\"1903\" height=\"1008\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/302/205/2020-06-27_21.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1113\" height=\"590\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/302/206/2020-07-11_18.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1113\" height=\"590\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/302/207/2020-06-27_21.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1113\" height=\"590\" /></p>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Strata cross sections</strong></span></p>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p><strong>Cross Section 1<br /></strong></p>\n<p><strong><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/295/532/2020-06-02_23.png\" /></strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Cross Section 2</strong></p>\n<p><strong><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/295/533/2020-06-03_00.png\" alt=\"Cross Section 2\" width=\"1903\" height=\"1008\" /></strong></p>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/joCZSo6.png\" width=\"1126\" height=\"18\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>⚠️ Bug:</strong></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"st\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\">Found a bug that's causing problems during launch or in game? Go to the Github Issues page of Strata and create a <strong><a href=\"https://github.com/Quizer9O8/Strata/issues/new?assignees=Quizer9O8&amp;labels=Bug%2C+Review&amp;template=bug_report.md&amp;title=\">Bug report</a></strong>.</span><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><br /></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/joCZSo6.png\" width=\"1126\" height=\"18\" /></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">💡<strong> Suggestion:<br /></strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span class=\"st\">Do you have an idea that would make Strata even better? Be the first one to mention this suggestion on the Github Issues page of Strata by creating a <a href=\"https://github.com/Quizer9O8/Strata/issues/new?assignees=Quizer9O8&amp;labels=Feature%2C+Review&amp;template=feature_request.md&amp;title=\"><strong>Feature request</strong></a>.</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><br /></span></p>\n\nIf you want to support me doing more of this stuff in the future I do have a Ko-fi page: https://ko-fi.com/quizer9o8",
